{"title":"英雄离我们很近","authors":["王永武"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":10,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄离我们很近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王永武"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄纪念碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碑是挺起脊梁的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人是血肉浇铸的碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耸立于天地之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个古老的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用最硬者的骨头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支撑起的一方苍穹上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一抹不逝的绚丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄们站在石碑的各个方位"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以缄默的姿式瞩望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听任雨打岁月而本色依旧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群寻踪而来的年轻军人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拜读屹立着的这册大书里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一种根须状的感觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延伸至骨髓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始觉葳蕤的生命之旅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远还没有结束"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群鸽子飞过碑的额头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨声悠扬而高亢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无名烈士墓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铅色砌一堵厚厚的墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔断两代军人握手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清晰地看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阻挡枪弹的躯体上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累累弹痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开着铜色的花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个壮烈激越的口号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洞穿浓重的黑夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔了几十年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铿锵的音韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹响耳畔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜血洗亮的白杨树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁大智慧的瞳孔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿然于无声的花丛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然闪现黎明的芳香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此执著地拥抱大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是真正地热爱生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柏树独守一方静土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地开花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是最开心的微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从生命的至高点上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注释忠诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名字已变得毫无意义"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}